Instead of the try catch you a better choice would be to add as a common parameter
    @Rule
    public ExpectedException exception = ExpectedException.none();

and in the tests expecting exception have:
        exceptionRule.expect(InvalidRouteConfigurationException.class);
        exceptionRule.reportMissingExceptionWithMessage("Duplicate routes shouldn't be accepted.");

